                            <comment id="13464839" author="alex.parvulescu" created="Thu, 27 Sep 2012 16:00:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I still wan&apos;t happy with the initial index state and added a few more tricks in rev 1391071.&lt;/p&gt;

